<subSubSection id="C3506566FF85972C6DADF97EEE03AD41" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="8BF536EDFF85972C6DADF97EEE03AD41" blockId="9.[151,1436,1760,2011]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
<emphasis id="B93EEAFFFF85972C6DADF97EEDA0ACFE" bold="true" box="[151,251,1760,1786]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Biology.</emphasis>
A large series of specimens was reared in 
<collectingCountry id="F35D767DFF85972C6E2EF97FEEC8ACFF" box="[788,915,1761,1787]" name="Guatemala" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
from flowerheads of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4A4D6EFF85972C6998F97FEC6CAD24" authority="(Jacq.) Sweet" authorityName="Sweet" baseAuthorityName="Jacq." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Pluchea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="carolinensis">
<emphasis id="B93EEAFFFF85972C6998F97FE8C7ACFE" box="[1186,1436,1761,1786]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Pluchea carolinensis</emphasis>
(Jacq.) Sweet
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName id="4C4A4D6EFF85972C6C73F898EC8BAD24" box="[329,464,1798,1824]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
: Inuleae), a new host plant record for this species. Five other species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4A4D6EFF85972C6806F898E8C7AD1B" box="[1340,1436,1798,1823]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Pluchea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B93EEAFFFF85972C6806F898E8C7AD1B" box="[1340,1436,1798,1823]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Pluchea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have been reported previously as host plants of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4A4D6EFF85972C6FFFF8B5EE0BAD40" baseAuthorityName="Snow" baseAuthorityYear="1894" box="[709,848,1835,1860]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Acinia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="picturata">
<emphasis id="B93EEAFFFF85972C6FFFF8B5EE0BAD40" box="[709,848,1835,1860]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">A. picturata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
